Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.13,0:01:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死在这里\N而我就抓紧荣耀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是输给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是输给飞翼零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输给区区这种系统…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.32,0:01:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十三话\N[孤独的战场]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常悦耳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你也有音乐天份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.65,0:02:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我自小就喜欢音乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弹奏乐器能令我的心平静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.33,0:02:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，听来好像是悲伤的乐曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别再责备自己比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战斗里也有迫不得已的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，那关乎人类的生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说迫不得已就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坚强一点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦就不会有那遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐，收到OZ的情报吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然特列斯大人仍然下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ和成为叛军的特列斯派的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在全世界激烈起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，战况对OZ有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为普通驾驶员追不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的机动性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为我们能和MD对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是自大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先要有钢弹般性能的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.98,0:03:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，即使出战消灭MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争也不会结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们亲身感受过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,区区一个驾驶员能做的事有限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下…山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能安慰那种士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的确是休息之地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，被血沾污的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许不可在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想希洛也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把在宇宙大量生产的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派落地球上\N纷争地域的新星作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稳步得到成效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人类亲眼目睹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的权力正在扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那意味着罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配体制的确立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲入大气层准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艇长，今次看来没阻碍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来值得庆幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是高热源反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是托尔吉斯!不会有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二号三号艇被毁!\N只剩下本艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动MD!迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全军覆没?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类没理由能战胜MD…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是[匹斯米利安]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容托尔吉斯后\N马上离开这空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是闪电伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我只懂得做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.27,0:06:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，霍华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小意思，我们只是尽点心力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我就恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拜托你再调整托尔吉斯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么?没受损吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，我总是觉得反应迟钝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为你的反应速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你在这么短时间内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有超越托尔吉斯机动性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要作为\N杰克斯‧马吉斯活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是为了山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他好像以山克王国大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上来宇宙，然后潜伏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真棘手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优候爵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那国家提倡的完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在仍得到很多国家的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不妙的是在财团里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.21,0:07:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那主义也正开始扩散开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.51,0:07:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉有无敌的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没必要有那种懦弱的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无敌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.22,0:07:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它被杰克斯‧马吉斯击败了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一个降下地点\N是卢森堡基地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，准备已经完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今次不会让\N杰克斯为所欲为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但愿如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.37,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也试试对付他的亲人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许应该趁这机会消灭她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你在这种地方吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以坐在旁边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.06,0:08:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随便你，这里是你的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你为何留在我的国家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是以前的你，我怎样阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也会马上前去战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.95,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你曾经回去宇宙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你的故乡没好好待你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很难过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希洛你也不能停止战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那双藏有辛酸的瞳孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和初次见到你时毫无分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.37,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰你们，对不起\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.98,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.42,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是罗姆斐拉财团的邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于OZ的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界的纷争即将解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.20,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于战争结束后来临的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想学习山克王国的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是，我们寄出邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.84,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出席在毕莱梅举行的聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.15,0:09:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恕我冒昧，我自荐负责引路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和莉莉娜殿下一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实感荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，请上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你，桃乐丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.27,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，没那必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为莉莉娜殿下是客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉会负责送她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐，拜托你看管这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，请你答应我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会瞒着我离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，要出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让她去没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对罗姆斐拉来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这国家的思想是危险的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一她有什么不测…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你打算做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大量MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即将降下卢森堡基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卢森堡有特列斯派的根据地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.18,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉想一次歼灭他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然一次过派这么多来地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卢森堡防卫多严密也支持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果赢了，如此一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD就会从那里扩展到全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!你多厉害也不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独自击落这么多MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你无论如何要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，你留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还不可以死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在找到特洛瓦之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.00,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，什么回事?\N希洛呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛选择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最有可能战死的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭一个基地来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,数量有点夸张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卢森堡就是那么重要的据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但用来对付闪电伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要那么多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使对手怎样攻来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只会全力战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卢森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前从联合抢回来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到今次要为了保护它而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.26,0:13:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讽刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，你果然出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有穿梭机别管托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲入大气层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何都要攻陷卢森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日承蒙各位邀请，多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能和你见面才感光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能为各位效劳，我与有荣焉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在就是你大显身手的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要令我失望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国能和平治国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确全靠各位的罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，各位的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在全世界发动战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同是罗姆斐拉的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会产生不同形式\N的结果呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为怎样使用力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由那个人的心决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果各位真的渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.95,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望各位\N以我的山克王国为参考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我准备好尽一切努力协助各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来还年轻却有坚定的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但山克王国之内看来有茅盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我解释吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.52,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人向我们OZ的部队展开攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.15,0:15:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给予我们重大的损失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自称是山克王国的大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他接触过卫星，但之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以杰克斯‧马吉斯的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.97,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘坐托尔吉斯，和我们OZ敌对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反应始终迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.02,0:15:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ敌对即是和罗姆斐拉敌对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.19,0:15:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以认为\N山克王国有野心吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个驾驶员现在也自称是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.27,0:16:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，他就不是我哥哥米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特家\N是最渴望和平的一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为其中一份子的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能会驾驶机动战士战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，他有何下场…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.85,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和山克王国无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.33,0:16:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，这看来是我们的误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就适当地亲手处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒杰克斯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.64,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怀疑山克王国一事，我道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，容我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国，果然棘手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好出色啊，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧我看中你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争果然不是由木偶先生进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要由人类进行才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，也要莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更加更加努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在就救你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王兄知道我会这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是选择了战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以杰克斯‧马吉斯的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,护卫的MD全军覆没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，目标的穿梭机降下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能攻陷卢森堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卢森堡，别被攻陷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是新型的MD吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹01?为何会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在卢森堡，战斗好像开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被他阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.49,0:18:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要代替希洛保护莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.33,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望是我杞人忧天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一莉莉娜殿下有什么不测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就没脸见杰克斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵队长\N刚才有匿名通讯来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它说莉莉娜殿下的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会被MD部队袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.64,0:18:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出于一片苦心也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擅自来接你，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧啊，帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看来神色凝重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚会上有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.66,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏根振作点!帕根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说着多漂亮的话也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我救不了任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧!我总是要别人拯救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要武力的和平有可能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平是不能战斗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痴人说梦吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你那样子\N我们怎办才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.99,0:20:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要走你自己相信的路
